**How to use**
```bash
Copy & Paste the code in your project

Install React

Install tailwaind (-optional)
```

Props

```bash
Label: String

inputType: String (text, number)

defaultVal:String

loading: Boolean (optional)

onSave( value: String | Number): method to excute a function with the new value for the parent.

required: boolean (optional) (default > False)

validationMessage: String (optional) (default > 'This field is required')  

updateBtnText: String(optional) (default > Update)

cancelBtnText: String(optional) (default > Cancel)

id:String | Number
```
